Paper: hep-th/9908057

Date: 1999-08-07

Title: Again on the possible compositeness of the photon

Comments: ReVTeX file, 19pp., no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Scripta 64 (2001) 119-127

We construct the transversal and longitudinal 4-vector potentials andstrengths F^{\mu\nu} in the momentum representation on using the second-type4-spinors recently proposed by Ahluwalia. Questions of relevance of this kindof theories to the correct photon statistics are briefly discussed.